  <brief_title>Prognostic and Diagnostic Value of Biomarkers and Cardiac Functional Parameters in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prognostic and Diagnostic Value of Serial Biomarker Measurements, Echocardiographic Techniques and Cardiopulmonary Function Tests in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
